<plot>Jeremías, a young shepherd, makes a strange discovery and the community sorcerer fortells an awful malediction. With the arrival of the terrorist group in the town, the prediction begins to be realized. Several weeks laters, when the army comes and Jeremías is accused of being involved with the terrorists, he has to escape to save his life. Lima, the Peruvian megalopolis, is the only place where he can hide. But once he is in the big city, he has to keep hiding. He has to learn to live in the "civilized" world. Victoria, a girl with a sweet face but a strange life, will try to conduct him through a path he has never imagined.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?394919</url></doc>
